description:
In my interview with bass legend Steve Swallow, I asked for his thoughts on how one goes about discovering their unique musical voice.

I love asking this question because everyone has a different way of getting there. Here is Steve's six minutes of exploring the topic.
fulltitle: Steve Swallow on finding one's own musical voice
